Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that chart back,\Nyou damn woman thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person fell from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a pretty neat experience I had!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Terrifying, Mysterious Power!\NCaptain Buggy, the Clown Pirate!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss! You came to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but they're all yours now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The girl got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay!\NHer boss is still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Tryin' to cover\Nfor your crony, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is there any place to eat around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwin' around, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bastard!\N--Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if they killed that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You beat people with sabers barehanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're that... who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a thief who steals from pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Nami!\NHey, wanna team up with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't feel like\Nteaming up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I treat you to some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They still haven't caught the thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:04:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-They should be pursuing her\Nas we speak, Captain Buggy! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the map get stolen\Nso easily in the first place?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when we're about to enter\Nthe Grand Line and go on a rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, the shack was unlocked,\Nso it was easy to take for foes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, it was easy to take for foes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who has a fake nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you find this nose funny?!\NJust like a fake nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge and all red?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-Here it comes...\N--T-The Devil Fruit power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Buggy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if someone defies me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A flashy death awaits them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll overlook your verbal slip-up\Nand forgive you just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get that map back! Screw up...\Nand you know what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live alone in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't live in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here ran away because of Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Then you're a sneak thief.\N--How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a thief who only\Nsteals from pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare me\Nto scumbag sneak thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a thief's a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is to earn 100 million Berries,\Nno matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need that much for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with a map of the Grand Line,\N100 million is a real possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map? Are you a navigator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much more skilled than\Nyour average navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's perfect!\NDo you wanna be our navigator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Our new pirate crew member!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I swore to the person\Nwho gave me this straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'd gather a crew\Nand become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I hate more\Nin this world than pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only like money and tangerines!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Be our navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! You find her?!\N--Can't find her anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that girl thief go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble if\Nwe don't get that chart back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta do something about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I might consider it\Nif you agree to certain conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come with\Nme to see Buggy the pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I tied up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just rope.\NIs there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well! I was hoping to\Nmeet other pirates! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thief got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of you are pathetic!\NDie flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thief from earlier\Ncame back on her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who stole the chart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've captured the thief,\NCaptain Buggy the Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your chart back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why the change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boss and I had a fight!\NI'm fed up with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me join your crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Buggy is angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna use his Devil Fruit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fed up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a flashily amusing girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!\NYou can join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infiltration successful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are so dumb\Nand easy to manipulate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I in a cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel great today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl! What name do you go by?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's hold a\Nwelcome party for Nami here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrate flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!\NThis party's in your honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep my eyes peeled for\Na chance to take the chart back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe I'll swipe all of\NBuggy's treasure too, while I'm at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... wanna eat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is flashily great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Prepare\Na Special Buggy Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All set, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's about to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observe the might of the Buggy Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:11:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Buggy-sama's\Nbeloved Buggy Balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy Balls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly flashy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Buggy Balls and Devil Fruit powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can conquer the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's\Ngonna rule the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see why you're sick of him, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He takes the world too lightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and misunderstands everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't put up with it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll give you a\NBuggy Ball to blow away your old boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll also serve to prove\Nyour loyalty to me. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, this is a welcoming party!\NLet's have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.\NThis is my style of welcoming party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't shoot, I'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I do shoot, I'll wind\Nup no better than pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Light it flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Don't wimp out on me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands are shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when you take\Non pirates with half-assed resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resolve to do what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill people like it's nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a pirate's resolve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The resolve to put your own life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, new chick!\NQuit bein' a tease!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you light it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?! What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I didn't mean to--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Apologizing won't fix things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Now you're saving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only did it because of the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't want to wind up\Nlike these inhuman pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates took the life\Nof a person dear to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd ever be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's why... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your ridicule to a minimum, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill her flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water! Water! Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many of you are\Ntaking on one girl at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you find us?\NHurry and get me outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you keep playing around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First some bird runs off with you,\Nand now you're inside a cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty interesting, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zoro"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's what he just called him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew member he mentioned...\Nwas Pirate Hunter Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want? Are you here\Nto take my head or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Not interested.\NI gave up pirate-hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested, though!\NKilling you will increase my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't try it. You'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess words aren't enough for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get 'im, Captain!\N--Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had no resistance to him at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? Their captain's been killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:19:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's so damn funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that arm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chop-Chop Fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the name of\Nthe Devil Fruit I ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a chop-chop person who can't be cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body reattached itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the\NDevil Fruits were only a rumor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A chop-chop guy?!\NYou mean he's a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rubber Person"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hit any vital spots,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's a pretty\Nserious wound! I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too much, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! The tables have turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do something quick,\Nme and these two guys are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one hurt a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stabbing him from behind is unfair,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot!\NDon't call him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's... got a big nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick my ass? You're a real riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of you are\Ngonna die here, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I have my ass\Nkicked in this situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! He came here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing makes sense anymore!\NThis is why I hate pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impudent fool!\NAs if I'd let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!\NYour Three-Sword Style has no effect on--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Listen when\Npeople are talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!\NThe cannon's pointed this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Light it!\N--Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry!\N--R-right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! There's still\Na Special Buggy Ball in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! No! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, don't worry. I'm better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:23:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?!\NYou can't possibly be better!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.48,0:24:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What an unfriendly dog!\N--I'm not referring to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.32,0:24:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!\NThere's a polar bear on top of a lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They followed you guys here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Desperate Situation!\NBeast Tamer Mohji vs. Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
